data.Title: Every Numbering
data.ShortDescription: This app allows users to define a unique automatically generated values for RecordSetItems, i.e., entries of a RecodSet.
data.Description: This app allows users to define a unique automatically generated values for RecordSetItems, i.e., entries of a RecodSet.
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Note Manager
data.ShortDescription: The EveryNoteManager is EveryDataStore's app that enables adding new or remove existing notes of individual RecordSetItems.
data.Description: The EveryNoteManager is EveryDataStore's app that enables adding new or remove existing notes of individual RecordSetItems. This app is available to admins for installation under the following path: Administration / Apps
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Multi Item Deletion
data.ShortDescription: This app allows front end users to delete multiple RecordSet items by selecting checkboxes in the result list.
data.Description: This app allows front end users to delete multiple RecordSet items by selecting checkboxes in the result list.
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Notify Template
data.ShortDescription: The EveryNotifyTemplate app allows users to design different styles of templates that can be filled out with data from EveryDataStore RecordSetItem.
data.Description: The EveryNotifyTemplate app allows users to design different styles of templates that can be filled out with data from EveryDataStore RecordSetItem. Therefore, print templates can be used to create a template for each RecordSet, but also to create report templates that will combine data from many different sources, i.e., different RecordSets and RecordSetItems.
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Widget
data.ShortDescription: Widgets are useful and visually appealing interface components for an easy access to certain information.
data.Description: Widgets are useful and visually appealing interface components for an easy access to certain information. Widgets are placed on the Dashboard. They can be activated or deactivated and arranged as desired.
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Version History
data.ShortDescription: The “EveryVersionHistory” is EveryDataStore's app that manages versions of RecordSets and RecordSetItems.
data.Description: The EveryVersionHistory shows information about all different versions of the Database and RecordSetItem, i.e., every time when an update happens within one Database and RecordSetItem, a new version is created.
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every EveryItemExportImport
data.ShortDescription: EveryItemExportImport allows use to import and export RecorSetItems and ModelItems
data.Description: EveryItemExportImport allows use to import and export RecorSetItems and ModelItems
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Filemanager
data.ShortDescription: EveryFileManager app is interfac for managing the EveryDataStore file system that allows users to uploading documents, images and other types of files to RecordSetItems
data.Description: EveryFileManager app is interfac for managing the EveryDataStore file system that allows users to uploading documents, images and other types of files to RecordSetItems
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Translator
data.ShortDescription: This App tranlates RecordSet form elements like labels, Info, default values, section name etc.
data.Description: EveryTranslator is EveryDataStore's app / plugin that manages languages and translates RecordSet form elements like label, Info, default values, section name etc. This app is available to admins for installation under the following menu: Administration/Apps
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH

data.Title: Every Defaul Folders
data.ShortDescription: This App EveryDefaulFolders creates for each RecordSetItem the same folder tree structure
data.Description: Should all RecordSetItems of a particular RecordSet have the same folder tree structure in their file manager, i.e., in the Documents tab, this structure can be set up in the Default Folders option under Administration menu by adding a new default folder
data.Author: EveryDataStore GmbH
